description:
This style is just minor tweaks I always make to <a href="https://userstyles.org/styles/144962/youtube-deepdark-material">YouTube DeepDark Material
by RaitaroH</a> so I can access the modifications quickly from other devices without having to start all over.

My Settings for YouTube DeepDark Material  are ...

		/*User colors*/
		--main-color: #ab0101;
		--main-background: #111111;
		--second-background: #181818;
		--hover-background: #232323;
		--main-text: #efefef;
		--dimmer-text: #9b9b9b;

...if you would like to have the same settings.

PLEASE NOTE: This style requires the <a href="https://userstyles.org/styles/144962/youtube-deepdark-material">YouTube DeepDark Material</a> style by RaitaroH to be installed!

css:
@-moz-document domain("youtube.com"), regexp("https?://(?!gaming.).*youtube.com/(?!premium).*$") {
ytd-watch-flexy {
    background: #101110 !important;
}

.title.ytd-video-primary-info-renderer {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 2.4rem;
}

#owner-name.ytd-video-owner-renderer {
    --yt-endpoint-color: var(--yt-channel-owner);
    --yt-endpoint-hover-color: var(--yt-channel-owner);
    font-size: 2.0rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 2.2rem;
}

ytd-user-mention-autosuggest-input {
    margin-right: 1.5rem;
}

ytd-commentbox:not([polymer2]) #contenteditable-textarea.ytd-commentbox {
    background: #191919;
    border: 1px solid #9b9b9b;
    color: #efefef;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 0.5rem 0.5rem 0.5rem 1rem;
}

#author-text.yt-simple-endpoint.ytd-comment-renderer {
    color: #3b3b3b !important;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 500;
}

ytd-compact-video-renderer #video-title.ytd-compact-video-renderer {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.6rem;
}

#items.yt-horizontal-list-renderer > .yt-horizontal-list-renderer:hover a.ytd-grid-video-renderer, ytd-compact-video-renderer:hover #video-title.ytd-compact-video-renderer, ytd-video-renderer:hover #video-title.ytd-video-renderer, ytd-playlist-renderer:hover h3.ytd-playlist-renderer, #content.ytd-playlist-video-renderer:hover #video-title, a.yt-simple-endpoint.ytd-playlist-panel-video-renderer:hover #video-title, .style-scope.ytd-grid-renderer.use-ellipsis:hover #video-title, #video-title:hover {
    color: #9b9b9b !important;
}

yt-formatted-string[ellipsis-truncate] a.yt-formatted-string:last-child, #byline.ytd-video-meta-block {
    font-weight: 800;
}
}
